  "title": "A Doll's House (No Relation)",
  "description": "Doll is a serial killer. Doll is an artist. Doll is an utter loser. They want to be great, the next BTK or Son of Sam. That's what this show is. A chance to convince you that they can be the next big thing. Will Doll be able to overcome their awkwardness and disturbing demeanour to do so? Not really. But they'll try.",
  "credits": "<strong>Playwright</strong>: Phoenix McLeod<br/><strong>Director</strong>: Phoenix McLeod<br/><strong>Cast</strong>: Madeline Podlubny<br/><strong>Designers</strong>: Annika Schultz<br/>",
  "website": "https://instagram.com/fuguestateprod",
  "plain_language": "A darkly funny one-man show starring Doll, who wants to be a famous serial killer. Doll is desperate to prove they’re brilliant, edgy, and the next big thing. They’ll rant, ramble, and reveal their crimes... but can they actually win you over? Probably not, but they will try!",
